column5: Some of you might have noticed a slowdown in board speed earlier this evening. Our server people received a greater than anticipated influx of traffic over the last 24 hours and this slowed us down temporarily. To correct the situation they have moved some people off the grid and will be moving a few more overnight. We should be good to go now.  Thanks for understanding.
Wow, whoda think it........ OFC is now becoming "pushy"  That is something to be proud of though, in a good way!  It gets any worse, you guys will just have create your own host  Cheers, Ron...
Awesome were now the bullies of the fishing Internet world and I thought it was some other board.
OFC's conquest to reign supreme over the interweb? Why not?
